Ok, I'm back.

::Striker::

Striker frowns as he recieves Spears' transmission. "Yes," he replies, "The 
Cybertronian Fire has plenty of spare parts. You might want to contact them."

He turns to Brix. "Hello, I'm Striker. Right now we need to work on the Ark a 
bit, later we might launch an attack against the Predacons."
